      "parameters": {
        "content": {
          "config": {
            "name": "How to use",
            "position": [
              -64,
              208
            ],
            "parameters": {
              "content": "# Populate lovestyle_prod row\n\nClick **Execute workflow** to upsert the `lovestyle_prod` row in `cs_project_config` with 35 values extracted from the LS prod workflows.\n\n## Columns left blank (fill manually in the table UI if needed)\n- `ticket_custom_field_automation_label_id` — no `automationCustomFieldID` passed to the ticket-update subworkflow in LS prod\n- `slack_dev_error_channel_id` — not applicable to a prod row\n- `refund_macro_monthly_legacy_id` — no legacy monthly macro in LS prod\n- `refund_value_monthly_alt`, `refund_value_30day_last_charge_alt` — no distinct alt strings in prod\n- `macro_thanks_reply_id`, `message_limit_threshold`, `macro_cancellation_confirmation`, `macro_refund_confirmation`, `macro_single_refund_complaint`, `macro_double_refund_complaint` — no `LS prod - 2nd message trigger` workflow exists yet\n\n## Pre-existing bugs in LS prod workflows (NOT fixed here, just flagged)\n- `LS prod - Zendesk tickets main automation flow v2` → `Set refund and cancellation vars`: `zendeskDomain=efuturechatbot` (should be lovestylehelp), `ticketCustomStatusID=33825964519453` (dev value)\n- `LS prod - Refund requests flow` → `Edit Fields1` (rejection_alt): `zendeskDomain=efuturechatbot`, `ticketCustomStatusID=33825964522269`, `ticketCustomFieldID=33838126178205` — all dev leftovers\n- `LS prod - Refund requests flow` → `Set refund and cancellation vars1`: `zendeskDomain=efuturechatbot`, `ticketCustomStatusID=19265567019421`\n- `LS prod - Refund requests flow` → `Edit Fields15` (upsell): `ticketCustomFieldID=33838126178205`, `ticketCustomStatusID=33825964522269` — dev leftovers\n\nThe templated versions reading from this table will use the CORRECT values regardless of the bugs above.\n\n## After running\nVerify the row in the data table view, then archive this workflow.",
              "height": 560,
              "width": 700,
              "color": 5
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
